description:
You are given a multiset $ S $ . Over all pairs of subsets $ A $ and $ B $ , such that:

- $ B \subset A $ ;
- $ |B| = |A| - 1 $ ;
- greatest common divisor of all elements in $ A $ is equal to one;

find the sum of $ \sum_{x \in A}{x} \cdot \sum_{x \in B}{x} $ , modulo $ 998\,244\,353 $ .
